rce/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8413585888208063, \"rank\": 0.18621093750812942, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 576, \"end\": 590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rebeca Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her total score\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 525}, {\"ngram\": \"a point\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 557}, {\"ngram\": \"the closest calls\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 626}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 632}, {\"ngram\": \"a major international event\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 680}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it was enough for the 27-year-old to win her second gold of the Paris Olympics and her sixth Olympic gold medal overall.\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 807, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her second gold\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 743}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 765}, {\"ngram\": \"her sixth Olympic gold medal\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 798}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles also broke boundaries by becoming the oldest woman to claim the biggest title in her sport since 1952.\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 917, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 814}, {\"ngram\": \"boundaries\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 836}, {\"ngram\": \"the oldest woman\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 865}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest title\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 892}, {\"ngram\": \"her sport\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 905}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The past 12 Olympic all-around women's champions were teenagers.\", \"from\"